cu.explanation_en: Changed tracking_area_code from 1 to 0, which is out of range for valid TAC values (must be between 1-65535), causing TAC configuration errors and preventing UE tracking area updates.

du.explanation_en: Changed tracking_area_code from 1 to 0, which is out of range for valid TAC values (must be between 1-65535), causing TAC configuration errors and preventing UE tracking area updates.
du.explanation_zh: 将tracking_area_code从1更改为0，这超出了有效TAC值的范围（必须在1-65535之间），导致TAC配置错误，从而阻止UE跟踪区域更新。
